7 An Act relating to public health and safety;
authorizing the State Commissioner of Health to
8 promulgate rules; authorizing local authorities to
regulate mobile food vendors; allowing administrative
9 hearing upon suspension or revocation of certain
license; establishing penalties; providing appeals
10 process; amending 63 O.S. 2021, Section 1-1101, which
relates to definitions; defining terms; amending 63
11 O.S. 2021, Section 1-1118, as last amended by Section
135, Chapter 452, O.S.L. 2024 (63 O.S. Supp. 2024,
12 Section 1-1118), which relates to food establishment
