19 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
20 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 1-1150 of Title 63, unless there
21 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
22 A. A mobile food vendor with a food establishment license
23 required under Section 1-1118 of Title 63 of the Oklahoma Statutes
24 is authorized to operate in this state subject to this section.
