2 act to the State Department of Health;
3 7. Issue citations and penalties to mobile food vendors for
4 violations of state and local law not inconsistent with this act;
5 and
6 8. Adopt and enforce other regulations in conformity to
7 municipal powers that are not inconsistent with this act. Any
8 regulation regarding mobile food vendors must address public health
9 or safety risks.
